{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-159-digital-root-sums-of-factorisations","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 159: Formula za digitalne korene distribucije","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mješoviti broj se može podijeliti na mnogo različitih načina.</p>\n<p>Na primer, bez uključivanja množenja sa jedni, 24 se može podeliti na 7 različitih načina:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 24 = 2 \\times 2 \\times 2 \\times 3\\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 2 \\times 3 \\times 4  \\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 2 \\times 2 \\times 6  \\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 4 \\times 6    \\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 3 \\times 8    \\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 2 \\times 12   \\\\\n&#x26; 24 = 24\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da se digitalni koren broja, u bazi 10, dobija sabiranjem cifara tog broja, i ponavljanjem tog procesa sve dok broj ne bude manji od 10. Dakle, digitalni koren 467 je 8.</p>\n<p>Naziva se Digitalni zbir korena (DRS) kao digitalni zbir korena ličnih komponenti našeg broja. Grafikon ispod prikazuje sve vrednosti DRS za 24.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Faktori</th>\n<th>Zbir digitalnog korena</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>2x2x2x3</td>\n<td>9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2x3x4</td>\n<td>9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2x2x6</td>\n<td>10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4x6</td>\n<td>10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3x8</td>\n<td>11</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2x12</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>24</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Najveći digitalni koren za 24 je 11. Funkcija $mdrs(n)$ vraća najveći digitalni koren za $n$. Dakle, $mdrs(24) = 11$.</p>\n<p>Traži $\\sum{mdrs(n)}$ za $1 &#x3C; n &#x3C; 1,000,000$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f40c1000cf542c50ff1e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301790,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-159-digital-root-sums-of-factorisations"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function euler159() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\neuler159();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>euler159()</code> treba da vrati <code>14489159</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(euler159(), 14489159);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-159-digital-root-sums-of-factorisations","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-160-factorial-trailing-digits","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-158-exploring-strings-for-which-only-one-character-comes-lexicographically-after-its-neighbour-to-the-left","id":"5900f40c1000cf542c50ff1e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-159-digital-root-sums-of-factorisations"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}